text: János Reznák (12 December 1930 - 11 June 1988) was a Hungarian wrestler. He competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics and the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1930 births Category:1988 deaths Category:Hungarian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Hungary Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:People from Cegléd
